  "text": "As suggested in a recent editorial [CITATION_1] , it seems important to avoid confusion between phenotypes and markers of disease severity (e.g., prognostic indices) or disease activity. Additionally, the recent update of the Global Initiative for Obstructive Lung Disease (GOLD) has introduced a new multidimensional classification of COPD, with four categories that could correspond to phenotypes.",
